      • answerDiff

        public AnswerElement answerDiff()
        The default implementation for generating differential answers.

        It uses TableDiff if the answer element is a TableAnswerElement. Otherwise, it uses a JSON-level diff.

        Answerers that want a custom differential answer, should override this function.
